condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Institutional Arrangements | Description :Borrower to cause the Project Implementing Entity (PIE) to carry outthe Project through the Project Implementing Unit (PIU) and inaccordance with the Project Agreements, operational Manual (OP),Environmental and Social Management Framework (ESMF) and not to amend the same, and to maintain PIU. | Due Date :30-Sep-2012
Finance Agreement :Mid-term Review | Description :Carrying out of mid-term review and preparation of reports before and after suchreview | Due Date :01-Sep-2014
Finance Agreement :Safeguards | Description :Borrower and PIE to comply with ESMF | Due Date :24-Oct-2012

Finance Agreement :Subsidiary Agreements | Description :Borrower to make loan proceeds available to PIE under Subsidiary Agreementsunder terms and conditions acceptable to World Bank | Due Date :12-Mar-2013
